channel.title: Paying someone to decompile/deob
channel.description:
Hi guys,
I've tried a few decompiling programs such as JODE, DJ, JD, JDEC
But have no luck with a sucessfully working decompile so it must be obfuscated.. Im willing to pay for a sucessful deob/decompile :) If anyone wants to give me a hand please reply here :) Here is one of the classes from 508 hd opengl client
http://rapidshare.com/files/358309294/Class43.class
If you manage to decompile this please either pm it to me or post it here, I will give you money and the rest of the class files!
Goodluck and lookin' forward to see what happens!
